'Fanculo.

834
01:14:41,085 --> 01:14:42,377
Merda.

835
01:15:08,478 --> 01:15:09,938
Terza.

836
01:15:59,816 --> 01:16:01,067
Cazzo!

837
01:16:35,100 --> 01:16:36,768
